<div class="title">Perfection</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=opiateboi&Exact=1">opiateboi</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; opiateboi. "Perfection: An Experience with Alcohol (exp34548)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 5, 2007. erowid.org/exp/34548</div>

